import { FC } from 'react' import { useSelector, useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { Container, Row, Col, Card } from 'react-bootstrap' import Navigation from '../components/Navigation' import { reset } from '../store/data' import { useHistory } from 'react-router-dom' const Home: FC = () => { const { user }: any = useSelector((state: any) => state.data) const { username } = user const dispatch = useDispatch() const history = useHistory() const logout = () => { dispatch(reset()) history.push('/') } return ( <>
Hello {username}, welcome!
This is your blogs!
) } export default Home
